Join you too to our crew of nice and funny pirates! Hurry up, the sailing ship is going to sail!

We created a completely new edition of our Crazyfingers app series, enriched with many wonderful features!

Intuitiveness and simplicity are the same as before but younger child will find many new features to have fun alone or with mom and dad.

The app features are:
 • colors palette: 10 colors to choose from, feel free to use your creativity or choose the rainbow button to use the original colors, the white color is the “rubber”;
 • it is possible to choose the brush size to be fast when coloring big surfaces or to paint little details;
• each drawing can be printed in such a way that it can also be coloured on paper;
 • special paint palette: choose from various funny shapes to create originals and uniques drawings of from some animated stickers to bring drawings alive;
 • good choice of original and funny drawings;
 • possibility of turning background music on and off;
 • eye - hand coordination;
 • fun and easy to use and play, just move the finger on the drawing!

Get in you too on the world of pirates and have fun with light-hearted companionship. You will find the thin pirate, an unusual cat pirate and unlikely mouse pirate.... but we cannot unveil every secret: discover them by yourself!

We wish you to have fun with our Pirates!
